---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — CalcStack by TechTools365"
  description="Privacy policy for CalcStack financial calculators. We respect your privacy and explain how we handle your data."
>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Last updated: April 14, 2026</p>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>CalcStack (calcstack.techtools365.com) is operated by TechTools365. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect and how we use it.</p>

    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <h3>Calculator Inputs</h3>
    <p>All calculations happen <strong>entirely in your browser</strong>. We do not send your financial inputs (salary, loan amount, investment details) to any server. Your data never leaves your device.</p>

    <h3>Analytics</h3>
    <p>We use privacy-respecting analytics to understand which calculators are popular and how to improve them. This may include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
      <li>Country and general region (not precise location)</li>
      <li>Device type and browser</li>
      <li>Referral source</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not track individual users across sessions or build personal profiles.</p>

    <h3>Cookies</h3>
    <p>We use minimal cookies:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for the site to function</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Help us understand site usage (can be blocked without affecting functionality)</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising cookies:</strong> If display ads are shown, our ad partners may set cookies to serve relevant ads</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We may use the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics / Ezoic:</strong> For site analytics and ad serving</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> For hosting and CDN</li>
      <li><strong>Affiliate partners:</strong> When you click an affiliate link, the partner's site has its own privacy policy</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>Some pages contain affiliate links. When you click these links and make a purchase or sign up, we may earn a commission. Affiliate links are always marked with <code>rel="nofollow sponsored"</code> and disclosed on the page.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We do not store any personal financial data. Analytics data is retained for up to 26 months and then automatically deleted.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Block cookies through your browser settings</li>
      <li>Use an ad blocker (our calculators work fine with ad blockers)</li>
      <li>Request deletion of any data we may have about you</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions: <strong>contact@techtools365.com</strong></p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy occasionally. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
